glosses: to benefit natural resources and economic values of another nation or state (see sömürge (“colony”))
to quaff, gulp down, swallow, devour
to suck in, draw inward (with mouth)

examples.text: Karısı onu öyle sömürdü ki... yıllarca çocuk nafakasını beş kuruşu olmayana kadar ödemek zorunda kaldı.
examples.translation: His wife fucked him over so badly, he was forced to pay child support until he had nothing to his name.

etymology:
From Ottoman Turkish سومرمك (sümürmek, “to quaff, to devour”), causative form of Proto-Turkic *simü-, *sümü-. It is sümürmek in some dialects.
Cognates
Cognate with Karakhanid [script needed] (simürmēk, “to gulp down, swallow”), Azerbaijani sümürmək (“to suck”), Bashkir һемереү (hemerew, “to drink”), Chagatai [script needed] (sümürmek, “to drink”), Chuvash сим (sim, “honey drink”), Kazakh сіміру (sımıru, “to drink in one gulp”), Uyghur سۈمۈرمەك (sümürmek, “to sip, suck in”), Uzbek simirmoq (“to draw, take in”).
